name: FoodAndNutritionRelatedHistoryGrouping
title: Food and Nutrition Related History Grouping
description: Includes all concepts in food and nutrition history. Select relevant concepts depending on the use case.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Food and nutrition related history includes the quality and adequacy of a person's food and nutrient intake, meal and snack patterns, diets and food modifications, and their eating environment as a component of a Nutrition Assessment.),(Data Element Scope: Data elements include an individualized nutrition history obtained by a nutrition professional across relevant care settings.),(Inclusion Criteria: Data included represents a portion of nutrition history assessment data used to determine an customized nutrition care plan.),(Exclusion Criteria: Data excluded is all assessment data that does not include nutrition specific history.)
